PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2013-12772013-11-21,  ,  ,  ,  ,  PWGSC
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCanada Lands Company Limited ** Corporate Plan **
PrecisOrder (1) approving the CANADA LANDS COMPANY LIMITED Corporate Plan 2012-2013; (2) approving the CANADA LANDS COMPANY LIMITED Corporate Plan for the Planning period from 2013-2014 to 2017-2018; (3) approving the leases set out in Appendices A and B of the 2013-2014 to 2017-2018 Corporae Plan, and the retention and use of the proceeds of the leases; and (4) amending Order in Council P.C. 2011-1253 of October 20, 2011, by replacing the reference to "the disposal of 16.2 acres of real property held by Parc Downsview Park Inc. in the Stanley Greene neighbourhood to Urbancorp Downsview Park Development Inc., Toronto, Ontario, and the retention and use of the proceeds" in paragraph (b), with a reference to "the disposal of 24 acres of real property held by Parc Downsview Park Inc. in the Stanley Greene neighbourhood to Urbancorp Downsview Park Development Inc., Toronto, Ontario, and the retention and use of the proceeds".
AttachmentsAttachment
